== Shimosuwa Dam Project ==
A dam project was originally proposed, but the plan was canceled following Governor {{ill|Yasuo Tanaka (politician)|en|Yasuo Tanaka (politician)|WD=Q706258|lt=Yasuo Tanaka|1=Yasuo Tanaka (politician)}}'s {{ill|No-Dam Declaration|ja|脱ダム宣言|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/No-Dam Declaration|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 中止したダム事業|1=Q11366307|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q11366307}} in Nagano Prefecture.

